Package org.cid15.aem.veneer.api

Interface Accessible

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    VeneeredPage, VeneeredResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractComponent
    public interface Accessible
    Definition of accessor methods for content resources for VeneeredResource and VeneeredPage instances.

      • get

        <T> Optional<T> get​(String propertyName,
                    Class<T> type)
        Get a property value from the current resource. This returns the same value as the underlying ValueMap wrapped in an Optional instance instead of returning null.
        Type Parameters:
        T - property type
        Parameters:
        propertyName - property name
        type - property type
        Returns:
        Optional of the given type containing the property value or absent if the property does not exist

        Optional<String> getAsHref​(String propertyName)
        Given a property on this resource containing the path of another resource, get an Optional containing the href to the resource (i.e. the content path with ".html" appended).
        Parameters:
        propertyName - name of property containing a valid content path
        Returns:
        href value wrapped in an Optional

      • getAsPage

        Optional<VeneeredPage> getAsPage​(String propertyName)
        Get a page instance from the value of the given property. Will return an absent Optional if the path value for the given property name does not resolve to a valid CQ page.
        Parameters:
        propertyName - property name
        Returns:
        Optional page for property value

      • getAsPageList

        List<VeneeredPage> getAsPageList​(String propertyName)
        Get a list of pages from the value of the given property. Pages will only be returned in the list if the paths resolve to a non-null page.
        Parameters:
        propertyName - property name
        Returns:
        list of pages for property value

      • getAsResource

        Optional<VeneeredResource> getAsResource​(String propertyName)
        Get an Optional resource instance for a property on this resource containing the path of another Resource.
        Parameters:
        propertyName - name of property containing a resource path
        Returns:
        Optional instance of the resource, or absent if either the property does not exist or does not resolve to a resource

      • getAsResourceList

        List<VeneeredResource> getAsResourceList​(String propertyName)
        Get a list of resource instances for a property on this resource containing an array of paths to other Resources.
        Parameters:
        propertyName - name of property containing resource paths
        Returns:
        list of resources, or empty list if either the property does not exist or the resources for the paths do not resolve

      • getAsType

        <AdapterType> Optional<AdapterType> getAsType​(String propertyName,
                                              Class<AdapterType> type)
        Get an Optional type instance for a property on this resource containing the path of another Resource.
        Type Parameters:
        AdapterType - adapter class that is adaptable from Resource
        Parameters:
        propertyName - name of property containing a resource path
        type - type to adapt from resource
        Returns:
        Optional instance of the specified type, or absent if either the property does not exist or the resource does not adapt to the provided type
